'''''The Nightingale's Prayer''''' ni film yo mu misiri yakozwe muri 1959 iyoborwa na Henry Barakat kandi ishingiye kuri novel y'umwanditsi ukomeye Taha Hussein . Irimo Faten Hamama na Ahmed Mazhar<ref>Egypt’s cinematic gems: The Nightingale’s Prayer | MadaMasr</ref><ref>The Nightingale's Prayer - MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › the-nightingales-prayer</ref> <ref>For the Love of Film (Noir) - A Nightingale's Prayer - The ... <nowiki>https://www.theculturist.com</nowiki> › home › for-the-love-of-f...</ref>.

Mu 1996, mugihe k'imyaka 100 ya Sinema yo muri Egiputa, iyi film yatoranijwe murimwe mu mafilime 150 meza yo muri Egiputa<ref>Nightingale's Prayer, The - Arab Film Distribution <nowiki>https://www.arabfilm.com</nowiki> › item_print</ref>. Yakiriye igihembo cyishimiwe n’ishuri rikuru ry’imashusho y’ubuhanzi n’ubumenyi kandi yatoranijwe  muri Filime nziza y’ururimi rw’amahanga mu bihembo bya 32 bya Academy, ariko ntiyemerwa nk'umukandida.<ref>Arab Cinema Series: The Nightingale's Prayer - Film ... <nowiki>https://www.filmindependent.org</nowiki> › events › arab-cinem...</ref> <ref>Margaret Herrick Library, Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences</ref> Yinjiye kandi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya 10 rya Berlin<ref>"Nightingale's Prayer" between Text and Image - Sada El balad <nowiki>https://see.news</nowiki> › nightingales-prayer-between-text-and...</ref> . 

